[thinking] **Considering exporter dependency**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering whether the logging exporter is a necessary dependency. It seems like `opentelemetry-exporter-logging` might not be transitive, which raises questions about whether the customizer will be called without it. I wonder if the customizer only sees the configured exporter when it actually exists. If we don’t use a named exporter, could it default to a Noop exporter? It seems I might need to add the logging dependency, but only if it's truly needed. I could also explore using the built-in OTLP instead.
